data.description: DVB Electronic Program Guide table builder
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
This module generates only part of the tables defined in the
    document ETSI EN 300 468 - Digital Video Broadcasting (DVB);
    Specification for Service Information (SI) in DVB systems

    As this is part of the DVB specification the namespace DVB is
    choosen inside the module.
